channel.title: About the Lounge category
channel.description:
This category is for discussions that are related to Axoloti generally but are not specifically about Axoloti. (please ensure it has some relevance to Axoloti, rather than general discussion)
Everyone can see the contents, but only trust level 1 and above can contribute.
